{"author":{"id":"4bb6c1767e50694cfde61856db22bf137d1651e8a0b5ca858c486db3dd02f280"},"ops":[{"type":3,"timestamp":1778696227,"nonce":"UBKwxpcVJHJmjJI2tPjZ27WqoTA=","message":"**Vel-RMSE-ratio and pos-RMSE-ratio values corrected after go-cue alignment fix (`06f7faf`).** **One winner-status flip.**\n\nTrial averaging in absolute trial time before the pairwise-RMSE step inflated both within-cell and across-cell pairwise RMSE because `centerout`'s target-on duration is randomised per trial (~150 ms smear). The fix re-locks each trial to its own go cue before the trial-axis collapse.\n\nHold drift, peak vel, TTP, and CV(peak vel) are scalar per-trial metrics and are unchanged.\n\n| Cell | Pre-fix vel-RMSE-ratio | Post-fix vel-RMSE-ratio | Pre-fix winner? | Post-fix winner? |\n|---|---:|---:|:---:|:---:|\n| gru__jerk | 1.129 | 1.054 | no | no |\n| gru__jerk_motor_pre | 0.461 * | 0.552 | **yes** | **no (flipped)** |\n| gru__jerk_smooth_high | 0.037 * | 0.040 * | yes | yes |\n| gru__jerk_motor_smooth_combo | 0.036 * | 0.042 * | yes | yes |\n| gru__jerk_loss_v_terminal | 0.882 | 0.989 | no | no |\n| gru__jerk_loss_historical | 1.131 | 1.133 | no | no |\n\n(*) = beats the \u003c 0.5 threshold.\n\n**Substantive impact:** `gru__jerk_motor_pre` flips from \"narrowly beats \u003c 0.5\" (0.461) to \"narrowly misses\" (0.552). The two clear winners (`gru__jerk_smooth_high` and `gru__jerk_motor_smooth_combo`) are unaffected — they remain decisive at ~0.04. The motor-pre cell should be re-read as \"close to threshold; not a clear winner\".\n\nThis matrix is already marked superseded by `f47abb1` (the two bug-fix re-runs landed on `f47abb1`), so the practical impact of the flip is limited to historical interpretation of this matrix's three-winner framing.\n\nFixed by commits `53362d9` / `0e14755` / `c7a7883` / `35769d1` on `feature/go-cue-alignment-fix`.","files":null}]}